; Coverage for textual_directives.cc commodity nomarket sub-directive parsing
; Note: nomarket does not prevent -V conversion using explicit P prices

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10

commodity EUR
    nomarket

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    100 EUR
    Assets:Cash

test bal Expenses -V
             $110.00  Expenses:Food
end test
